fields.value: A dataset pertaining to the sex-dependent effects of preconception exposure to arsenite on gene transcription in parental germ cells and on transcriptomic profiles and diabetic phenotype of offspring

dsDescriptionValue.value: RNA sequencing was conducted to evaluate transcriptional status in sperm and oocytes of C57BL/6J mice exposed to 200ppb of sodium arsenite. Gene expression was also evaluated in off spring livers and islets that were exposed to inorganic arsenic prior to conception.
